gameRecap.title: Game Recap: Magic 124, Nuggets 119
gameRecap.excerpt: The Magic have won 5 consecutive games as they defeat the Nuggets, 124-119. Franz Wagner recorded a team-high 27 points, along with four assists for the Magic, while Paolo Banchero added 23 points, three rebounds, and four assists in the victory. Nikola Jokic tallied 30 points, 13 rebounds, and 12 assists for the Nuggets in the losing effort, the 111th triple-double of his career, and 6th of the season. The Magic improve to 10-5 on the season, while the Nuggets fall to 10-5.
